::GoldenEye::

She hugged Dollen, not sure about what to do. "I'm here for you love, 
no matter what."  She was actually getting scared for Dollen.  His 
behavior had changed so drastically in just the past few days.  She 
was getting more and more worried for him. "Listen, why don't we join 
the others. Perhaps Phobia can help you. But I shall stay st your 
side no matter what." She held him close and tried to comfort him as 
best as she could.
